column5: Hey i decided to take tuesday off and go jumbo hunting...managed to get more than a few with a mess of 10 inchers lossed into the mix.
Good luck out there this Sunday, Ray....hope they are still on that spot for ya
Thanks Jonny  I like to fish on tuesdays and sundays...if your around let me know  I may have to blind fold you and take away your GPS
LOLOL sounds good...don't mind me if I count the footsteps then
That's why he makes you walk in a big circle for and hour first.  Nice jumbos!
